modName: NEW SPELLS-Conjure Ice Wraith_ Conjure Magic Anomaly
summary: More Conjuration? Summon An Ice Wraith or a Magic Anomaly
descriptionHtml:
This is my first and most simple mod. This adds two new conjuration spells to the game, giving you the ability to conjure an Ice Wraith and Magic Anomaly. The two books are found in Dragon Reach underneath the kitchen were the kids are sitting ontop of an end table. Please like, endorse and comment. If so I\'ll be sure to make more mods! Thank you!

Check out my other mod Conjure Drakes
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12685
author: CHEIMON
